(c) The contract should provide for continuous monitoring and assessment by the
HFC of the service provider so that any necessary corrective measure can be
taken immediately;

(e) Controls to ensure customer data confidentiality and service providers' liability in
case of breach of security and leakage of confidential customer related
information should be incorporated;

When a person is considering being a guarantor to a loan, they should be informed
